<section class="container intro">
<h2>Professional geoportal</h2>
  <p>
    Our 100% open source geoportal solution is based on <a href="https://github.com/geoadmin/mf-geoadmin3">mf-geoadmin3</a>,
    a bunch of open source components created by Swisstopo, the Swiss Federal Office of Topography, and used on portal <a href="https://map.geo.admin.ch">map.geo.admin.ch</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
  This modern product is based on the current web technologies <strong>(HTML5, JavaScript, CSS3)</strong>.
  It works with <strong>all the major web browsers</strong> (Firefox, Chrome, Safari and Internet Explorer >= 10).
  The interface is also responsive and compatible with <strong>desktop computers, smart-phones and tablets</strong>.
  </p>
  <p><b>geoportal.xyz</b> solutions are able to be used with a unique and simple geoportal, but in 
  multi-geoportals and multi-customers contexts too.
  </p>
</section>

